1
00:00:00,440 --> 00:00:02,210
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:02,210 --> 00:00:03,680
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,680 --> 00:00:05,140
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:07,750 --> 00:00:10,350
Luckily, the call
was recorded and saved.

5
00:00:10,350 --> 00:00:13,390
You can hear Mr. Choi say
that Park Tae Ho ordered everything.

6
00:00:14,450 --> 00:00:15,590
I should release this...

7
00:00:15,590 --> 00:00:17,520
and ask the police
to reopen the investigation.

8
00:00:18,320 --> 00:00:19,320
Jin Ju.

9
00:00:20,490 --> 00:00:22,930
Even if you go to the police,
if Park Tae Ho pulls some strings,

10
00:00:23,230 --> 00:00:24,360
there's no telling
what might happen.

11
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:26,300
You worked so hard
to get this evidence,

12
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:27,370
and you could lose it.

13
00:00:28,730 --> 00:00:31,640
What if we tried using this
in a different way?

14
00:00:32,440 --> 00:00:33,770
A different way?

15
00:00:34,610 --> 00:00:36,880
I'm not taking the fall
for Chairman Park.

16
00:00:37,210 --> 00:00:40,110
I'm going to tell the truth
that he ordered everything.

17
00:00:43,350 --> 00:00:44,350
What?

18
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:46,120
(Choi Sam Sik)

19
00:00:46,180 --> 00:00:49,450
Wait. What is this?

20
00:00:50,160 --> 00:00:51,490
How can a dead man...

21
00:00:53,790 --> 00:00:57,130
Hello? Who are you?
Tell me who you are!

22
00:00:58,500 --> 00:01:00,330
It's a file
from Choi Sam Sik's phone.

23
00:01:00,770 --> 00:01:03,800
If you want to get rid of it,
do as I say.

24
00:01:04,470 --> 00:01:06,740
Wait. What?

25
00:01:09,740 --> 00:01:10,740
What the...

26
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:20,720
Prepare ten million dollars
for this file.

27
00:01:21,620 --> 00:01:23,490
Wait, ten million dollars?

28
00:01:24,390 --> 00:01:26,830
We'll exchange the money
for the phone tomorrow.

29
00:01:27,490 --> 00:01:30,130
I'll send you the time and place.
Be there.

30
00:01:30,430 --> 00:01:31,560
If you don't show up,

31
00:01:31,900 --> 00:01:33,900
I'll go straight to the police
and the press.

32
00:01:34,330 --> 00:01:37,400
If you try any funny business,
I'll release it then too.

33
00:01:38,170 --> 00:01:39,740
So don't even think about
trying to trick me.

34
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:42,140
(Park Tae Ho)

35
00:01:57,120 --> 00:02:00,560
How did the contents
of Choi Sam Sik's phone get leaked?

36
00:02:03,030 --> 00:02:04,030
Choi Yu Na...

37
00:02:05,100 --> 00:02:06,260
Choi Yu Na!

38
00:02:11,700 --> 00:02:15,470
Hyun Jun.
You haven't spoken to me in days.

39
00:02:16,270 --> 00:02:17,680
Stop being angry.

40
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:20,380
The chairman position at Adele Group
is within your grasp.

41
00:02:20,450 --> 00:02:23,050
What choice do you have
but to follow Chairman Park's orders?

42
00:02:23,050 --> 00:02:24,220
That's why...

43
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:28,120
I'm putting up
with this ridiculous situation.

44
00:02:29,450 --> 00:02:32,290
How much more do I have to endure
to get Adele Group?

45
00:02:32,420 --> 00:02:33,860
What am I...

46
00:02:35,790 --> 00:02:37,760
to Chairman Park Tae Ho anyway?

47
00:02:39,330 --> 00:02:41,870
Still, I'm trying my best
to endure it.

48
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:43,940
There's no need
to be so serious about it.

49
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:47,310
Just go through with the ceremony
as a formality.

50
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:50,440
We have to register
the marriage too.

51
00:02:53,980 --> 00:02:55,750
I'm not like Baek Jin Ju.

52
00:02:56,110 --> 00:02:57,220
I care more about...

53
00:02:57,220 --> 00:02:59,250
the marriage certificate
than the wedding ceremony.

54
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:03,590
More than a wedding dress,
the legal status is more valuable.

55
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:05,390
You really have no shame.

56
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,730
After barging in here
demanding to get married,

57
00:03:07,730 --> 00:03:09,760
you're setting yourself up
in Min Jun's old room?

58
00:03:10,530 --> 00:03:11,900
To get what I want,

59
00:03:12,460 --> 00:03:14,070
I have to endure
a little discomfort.

60
00:03:15,330 --> 00:03:16,330
Park Hyun Jun,

61
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:19,600
if you really want to be chairman,
stop avoiding this and just take it.

62
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:24,010
Why let your pride get in the way
when you need my shares?

63
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:26,040
It's not a matter of pride.

64
00:03:28,810 --> 00:03:30,210
I just have a weak stomach.

65
00:03:31,850 --> 00:03:34,420
I won't just swallow anything
to become chairman.

66
00:03:34,990 --> 00:03:37,020
What? "Just anything?"

67
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,860
Didn't I make it clear that you
make me sick...

68
00:03:38,860 --> 00:03:40,360
and give me the creeps?

69
00:03:40,860 --> 00:03:41,860
And above all,

70
00:03:42,530 --> 00:03:44,430
how long do you think
Father will put up with you?

71
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,970
I'm not so sure about that either.

72
00:03:48,670 --> 00:03:52,570
Choi Yu Na, get down here right now.
Choi Yu Na!

73
00:03:55,670 --> 00:03:56,670
See?

74
00:03:58,210 --> 00:04:00,910
Looks like another problem popped up
after just a few days.

75
00:04:01,650 --> 00:04:03,980
I know. What is it this time?

76
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:16,760
What is this about?

77
00:04:16,890 --> 00:04:19,500
Did you know your father made a call
right before going into...

78
00:04:20,730 --> 00:04:22,100
the interrogation room?

79
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:25,270
My dad made a call?

80
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:29,410
Oh my, you did the right thing.

81
00:04:30,610 --> 00:04:32,040
You made the right choice.

82
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:35,410
Since you've changed your mind,

83
00:04:35,910 --> 00:04:38,220
Jin Ju is going to forgive us.

84
00:04:40,820 --> 00:04:43,450
No, I wasn't aware of that.

85
00:04:45,590 --> 00:04:47,730
I'd think twice before lying.

86
00:04:48,730 --> 00:04:50,160
You always give yourself away.

87
00:04:51,130 --> 00:04:52,530
Give me a straight answer!

88
00:04:55,930 --> 00:04:58,870
All I knew was that
he made one final call.

89
00:04:59,470 --> 00:05:02,240
I had no idea what it was about,
so that's why I said I didn't know.

90
00:05:02,970 --> 00:05:05,040
Go to your mother right now
and confirm it.

91
00:05:05,410 --> 00:05:07,850
Ask her what they spoke about
on that call...

92
00:05:07,850 --> 00:05:09,280
and where his phone is now.

93
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,880
Immediately.

94
00:05:11,750 --> 00:05:13,420
Why are you being like this
all of a sudden?

95
00:05:13,790 --> 00:05:17,560
Yes, just tell us
what's going on first.

96
00:05:19,660 --> 00:05:23,330
Some guy called me
from Choi Sam Sik's phone.

97
00:05:23,830 --> 00:05:27,100
He said there was a recording
of a call on it.

98
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:31,040
A recording of Choi Sam Sik
stating he'd confess...

99
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:33,470
that he acted on orders from me.

100
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:37,040
He's using it to blackmail me
for ten million dollars.

101
00:05:37,580 --> 00:05:39,180
What? Ten million dollars?

102
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:40,680
You're being blackmailed?

103
00:05:41,010 --> 00:05:42,310
Just how...

104
00:05:43,010 --> 00:05:45,320
That's why you need to go
and confirm it right now.

105
00:05:46,420 --> 00:05:48,190
Yes, I'll check on it right away.

106
00:05:51,760 --> 00:05:52,960
Hold on.

107
00:05:53,730 --> 00:05:55,290
What happens if this gets out?

108
00:05:55,860 --> 00:05:58,800
I thought it was all over.
Will you be arrested again?

109
00:05:59,130 --> 00:06:01,530
Tell Manager Kang
to come in here right now.

110
00:06:01,830 --> 00:06:03,870
And get Detective Yun
here immediately!

111
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:18,180
Mom.

112
00:06:21,820 --> 00:06:23,050
Where's Dad's cell phone?

113
00:06:25,020 --> 00:06:26,090
And who might you be?

114
00:06:26,460 --> 00:06:28,790
Who do you think you are,
barging into my house...

115
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:31,400
and demanding
my husband's cell phone?

116
00:06:32,530 --> 00:06:35,570
What did Dad say
when you last spoke to him?

117
00:06:36,100 --> 00:06:37,970
Is it true he said
he'd reveal everything...

118
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,340
Chairman Park ordered him to do?

119
00:06:40,140 --> 00:06:43,070
Well, I have no idea
what you're talking about.

120
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:48,810
Don't tell me you're the one
who used Dad's phone as leverage.

121
00:06:49,310 --> 00:06:50,880
If so, you're in big trouble.

122
00:06:51,420 --> 00:06:52,520
Give me Dad's phone right now.

123
00:06:53,250 --> 00:06:54,920
I told you to make some sense.

124
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:57,820
Why are you looking
for your dad's phone?

125
00:06:58,820 --> 00:07:00,930
Never mind, I'll find it myself.

126
00:07:03,900 --> 00:07:06,730
You silly brat. Unbelievable.

127
00:07:11,370 --> 00:07:14,310
Hey, everyone,
come and look at this.

128
00:07:14,540 --> 00:07:16,810
A thief has broken into my house!

129
00:07:16,970 --> 00:07:20,610
What's gotten into you?
Do you want to see me go crazy?

130
00:07:21,810 --> 00:07:22,810
In that case,

131
00:07:23,410 --> 00:07:26,080
do you think
your behavior right now is normal?

132
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:28,690
Did you lose your mind ages ago?

133
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:32,360
Just tell me where Dad's phone is.
Where is it?

134
00:07:32,420 --> 00:07:33,890
How am I supposed to know that?

135
00:07:34,790 --> 00:07:36,390
I didn't receive anything
from the police station.

136
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:38,700
You didn't receive anything?

137
00:07:39,300 --> 00:07:41,000
They must've sent you
Dad's personal effects.

138
00:07:41,370 --> 00:07:42,370
I don't know.

139
00:07:43,130 --> 00:07:45,540
I was too busy with the funeral
to think straight.

140
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:49,240
I guess it must've disappeared
somewhere along the way.

141
00:07:54,010 --> 00:07:56,450
Please keep this a secret
from Yu Na.

142
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:02,320
Of course.

143
00:08:03,220 --> 00:08:05,890
If Yu Na finds out
about this recording,

144
00:08:06,460 --> 00:08:08,430
she'll try to get rid of it
no matter what.

145
00:08:10,330 --> 00:08:13,760
With this,
I'll prove Mr. Choi's innocence...

146
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:16,400
and make sure Park Tae Ho
is brought to justice.

147
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:18,270
Okay.

148
00:08:19,670 --> 00:08:21,070
You stepped up...

149
00:08:22,210 --> 00:08:24,210
to do the things
I couldn't do, Jin Ju.

150
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:27,510
I'm truly grateful to you.
Thank you.

151
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:45,160
You little brat. Give that back.

152
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:48,100
Unbelievable.

153
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,870
There's no recording on your phone.

154
00:08:51,300 --> 00:08:53,500
Then it must really be
on Dad's phone.

155
00:08:53,570 --> 00:08:56,740
You little thief.
Get out of here right now.

156
00:08:57,010 --> 00:09:00,110
If you don't leave,
I swear I'm calling the police.

157
00:09:00,180 --> 00:09:02,510
Don't worry. I'm leaving.

158
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:06,020
Just call me
when you find Dad's phone.

159
00:09:17,730 --> 00:09:20,300
You couldn't be bothered to go
to your own father's funeral,

160
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:23,600
but his picture made you freeze?

161
00:09:24,700 --> 00:09:27,140
I only didn't go
because you told me not to.

162
00:09:31,310 --> 00:09:32,380
Yu Na.

163
00:09:34,250 --> 00:09:36,150
It's still not too late.

164
00:09:36,950 --> 00:09:38,480
Even now...

165
00:09:43,050 --> 00:09:44,090
Choi Yu Na.

166
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:48,860
The funeral's over, so that's that.

167
00:09:49,190 --> 00:09:50,360
You've got...

168
00:09:51,260 --> 00:09:52,760
to let it go and move on, Mom.

169
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,310
Oh, Sam Sik.

170
00:10:07,980 --> 00:10:10,010
What am I supposed to do?

171
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:15,320
Goodness. What am I going to do
with that girl?

172
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:19,320
Gosh, Sam Sik.

173
00:10:20,930 --> 00:10:23,390
Just take me with you.

174
00:10:24,530 --> 00:10:27,000
I just don't have the strength
to go on.

175
00:10:27,370 --> 00:10:30,670
Sam Sik, what do I do?

176
00:10:36,170 --> 00:10:40,280
So the police
never handed over the phone?

177
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:43,450
Yes, that's what my mother said.

178
00:10:45,180 --> 00:10:48,250
The only person at the station
who could've intercepted it...

179
00:10:49,890 --> 00:10:51,390
is Chief Deputy Yun.

180
00:10:51,690 --> 00:10:52,690
What?

181
00:10:53,290 --> 00:10:55,090
Who are you accusing?

182
00:10:55,190 --> 00:10:58,360
Why not? You know the situation,
and you're greedy.

183
00:10:58,430 --> 00:11:00,000
You fit the profile perfectly.

184
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,770
Are you kidding me?

185
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:03,530
Why not just pay me...

186
00:11:03,530 --> 00:11:05,770
the ten million dollars
the blackmailer wants?

187
00:11:05,900 --> 00:11:08,040
I'll pass it around...

188
00:11:08,110 --> 00:11:10,810
and make sure that
if that recording comes out,

189
00:11:10,810 --> 00:11:12,240
no one believes it's real.

190
00:11:12,540 --> 00:11:15,710
And if you take the money
and fail, then what?

191
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:17,820
So you'd rather burn
ten million dollars...

192
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:19,280
on someone you don't even know?

193
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:34,600
Park Tae Ho.

194
00:11:35,330 --> 00:11:37,770
He must be agonizing over
what to do right now.

195
00:11:38,540 --> 00:11:40,340
Ten million dollars
is a lot of money.

196
00:11:40,370 --> 00:11:42,270
Will he really do what we expect?

197
00:11:42,810 --> 00:11:46,110
He's already spent a fortune
trying to cover this up.

198
00:11:46,210 --> 00:11:49,310
If the recording gets out now,
the damage will be immense.

199
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:52,150
He'll have no choice
but to make the deal.

200
00:11:52,350 --> 00:11:53,380
Right.

201
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:56,550
I just hope Manager Kang
is thinking the same thing.

202
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:04,100
Still, I think we should go
to the meeting place.

203
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:10,100
As I reported, we've already spent
over 20 million dollars.

204
00:12:10,770 --> 00:12:12,740
If the recording gets out,

205
00:12:12,740 --> 00:12:14,710
that 20 million dollars
will have been for nothing.

206
00:12:14,770 --> 00:12:16,310
And the circumstances
surrounding the murders...

207
00:12:16,370 --> 00:12:19,780
of Baek Jun Gi and Choi Sam Sik
will all come to light.

208
00:12:23,780 --> 00:12:25,820
Let's go to the meeting place.

209
00:12:26,420 --> 00:12:28,790
What? You want to hand over
ten million dollars?

210
00:12:29,090 --> 00:12:30,490
We'll go to the meeting place.

211
00:12:32,090 --> 00:12:33,760
We can lie in wait and catch them.

212
00:12:34,330 --> 00:12:36,830
Right, that's a good idea.

213
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:41,570
- That's my son for you.
- What a pain in my butt.

214
00:12:42,030 --> 00:12:45,040
If you're asking for my help again,
I'm going to need a big...

215
00:12:45,100 --> 00:12:46,570
You...

216
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:47,810
stay out of it.

217
00:12:49,940 --> 00:12:52,080
Hyun Jun and I
will catch them ourselves.

218
00:12:52,140 --> 00:12:53,140
All right?

219
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:58,680
We'll see how well you do
without my help.

220
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:03,750
All right. Park Hyun Jun,
you take the lead on this.

221
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:08,130
But first, make sure
Kim Dan Hui and Baek Jin Ju...

222
00:13:08,190 --> 00:13:11,100
aren't the ones behind this.

223
00:13:11,100 --> 00:13:13,330
I'll look into it. sir.

224
00:13:14,770 --> 00:13:16,700
- Be sure.
- Of course.

225
00:13:17,030 --> 00:13:18,300
If I solve this problem,

226
00:13:19,340 --> 00:13:20,570
I expect something in return.

227
00:13:21,870 --> 00:13:22,870
In return?

228
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:25,640
You can't ask to call off
the wedding.

229
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,110
Park Min Jun.

230
00:13:29,210 --> 00:13:31,780
It bothers me that he's still
at the company.

231
00:13:32,150 --> 00:13:33,450
Kick Min Jun out...

232
00:13:33,820 --> 00:13:36,350
and make it clear to everyone
that I'm your son...

233
00:13:37,290 --> 00:13:38,490
and heir.

234
00:13:40,090 --> 00:13:44,030
That's all you want from me
in return?

235
00:13:44,330 --> 00:13:45,330
Yes.

236
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:49,670
I want to be, solely and completely,

237
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:53,170
your son.

238
00:14:11,890 --> 00:14:14,530
Yes, Butler Ok. Thank you.

239
00:14:17,430 --> 00:14:18,560
How did it go?

240
00:14:18,860 --> 00:14:21,000
Park Tae Ho took the bait.

241
00:14:22,270 --> 00:14:25,040
Great. Then we should get ready.

242
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:28,210
My heart is racing like crazy.

243
00:14:29,010 --> 00:14:30,240
Don't worry.

244
00:14:30,610 --> 00:14:32,280
I'll be sure to protect you.

245
00:14:32,340 --> 00:14:33,410
Nonsense.

246
00:14:33,680 --> 00:14:37,080
This time, I'll make sure
to protect you, Yoon Jung.

247
00:14:45,690 --> 00:14:49,930
What? Why?
Why is everyone staring at us?

248
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,030
Well...

249
00:14:53,700 --> 00:14:55,630
I think they're onto us.

250
00:15:00,340 --> 00:15:01,410
We...

251
00:15:05,180 --> 00:15:07,380
have decided to protect each other.

252
00:15:10,310 --> 00:15:13,420
Everyone's so busy
dealing with Park Tae Ho,

253
00:15:13,820 --> 00:15:15,450
and this is thoughtless of us.

254
00:15:15,590 --> 00:15:17,860
I already knew.

255
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:21,830
- Really?
- I suspected as much.

256
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:25,960
- Really?
- I was waiting for you to tell us.

257
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:27,100
Dan Hui, you too?

258
00:15:28,030 --> 00:15:32,870
Yoon Jung, I'm so glad
you're with such a wonderful person.

259
00:15:34,170 --> 00:15:36,710
You'll take good care
of our Yoon Jung, won't you?

260
00:15:36,810 --> 00:15:39,010
Yes, I'll do my best.

261
00:15:39,010 --> 00:15:42,080
And of course, I'll give it my all
to make sure our plan succeeds.

262
00:15:42,350 --> 00:15:44,720
Of course. Just trust us.

263
00:15:45,180 --> 00:15:47,820
Still, you both need to be careful.

264
00:15:47,890 --> 00:15:50,990
Right. You two be careful, too.

265
00:15:56,830 --> 00:15:58,030
Do we look good together?

266
00:16:01,070 --> 00:16:02,470
(Adele)

267
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:13,210
So this is the meeting place?

268
00:16:13,610 --> 00:16:14,610
That's right.

269
00:16:14,910 --> 00:16:18,450
Geun Tae checked ahead
and said everything looked normal.

270
00:16:18,680 --> 00:16:20,280
I've already placed our men,

271
00:16:20,350 --> 00:16:22,320
and Manager Kang
will bring the money.

272
00:16:22,990 --> 00:16:24,120
What about their side?

273
00:16:26,290 --> 00:16:28,530
It doesn't seem like Kim Dan Hui
was the one who blackmailed us.

274
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:30,860
Ms. Choi's been following her,

275
00:16:31,560 --> 00:16:32,960
and she, Baek Jin Ju,
and Park Min Jun...

276
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:35,400
are still protesting
at the police station.

277
00:16:37,700 --> 00:16:39,000
(Police)

278
00:16:39,070 --> 00:16:40,670
(The Reinvestigation Must Continue!
Park Tae Ho Is Guilty!)

279
00:16:40,740 --> 00:16:42,570
(Murderer Park Tae Ho!
Investigate Thoroughly!)

280
00:16:48,580 --> 00:16:51,480
It's hot out.
Don't you think you should stop?

281
00:16:51,950 --> 00:16:54,920
- You think this will work?
- Are you that nervous?

282
00:16:57,020 --> 00:16:58,020
Nervous?

283
00:16:58,620 --> 00:17:00,320
- Me?
- If that isn't it,

284
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:02,630
then why are you
tailing us everywhere?

285
00:17:02,630 --> 00:17:04,630
I'm on an errand for the chairman.

286
00:17:05,330 --> 00:17:06,330
Or rather,

287
00:17:07,060 --> 00:17:09,270
should I say for my father-in-law?

288
00:17:09,600 --> 00:17:10,600
Father-in-law?

289
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:14,810
Because Park Hyun Jun was part
of my reward.

290
00:17:15,970 --> 00:17:17,170
We're getting married soon.

291
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:19,310
Actually, no.

292
00:17:19,610 --> 00:17:21,010
We're going
to register our marriage.

293
00:17:22,010 --> 00:17:23,010
What?

294
00:17:23,580 --> 00:17:27,650
When Park Hyun Jun becomes chairman,
I become the lady of Adele Group.

295
00:17:28,320 --> 00:17:30,150
That was your original plan,
wasn't it?

296
00:17:30,550 --> 00:17:34,960
That is, before you dumped him
for not being the chairman's son.

297
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:37,760
Dumped him? Don't you dare say that.

298
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:40,260
I'm going to make Park Hyun Jun
the chairman,

299
00:17:40,460 --> 00:17:41,970
even if he's not the chairman's son.

300
00:17:42,570 --> 00:17:45,970
I'll make it so he's untouchable,
even if his secret gets out.

301
00:17:48,510 --> 00:17:49,510
Just you watch.

302
00:17:50,070 --> 00:17:53,810
I'll be the one
to take over Adele Group.

303
00:18:00,080 --> 00:18:03,890
Something like this
won't be enough to stop me.

304
00:18:14,870 --> 00:18:16,730
If you had
my father's call recording,

305
00:18:16,730 --> 00:18:18,170
you wouldn't be doing this.

306
00:18:19,100 --> 00:18:21,410
At least it's not
Kim Dan Hui or Baek Jin Ju.

307
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:34,850
Did the news
of Hyun Jun getting married get to you?

308
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:37,890
No, it's not that.

309
00:18:40,660 --> 00:18:43,330
For now, I think
we've avoided suspicion with this.

310
00:18:44,190 --> 00:18:47,360
Let's keep at it a little longer
until we can snatch the money.

311
00:18:51,740 --> 00:18:52,870
Hyun Jun...

312
00:18:53,570 --> 00:18:55,740
won't fall for Choi Yu Na so easily.

313
00:19:14,190 --> 00:19:15,590
We should get going too.

314
00:19:16,860 --> 00:19:18,030
But, son...

315
00:19:19,860 --> 00:19:23,230
Why did you ask
for that kind of reward?

316
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:27,940
It would've been more beneficial
to ask for shares.

317
00:19:28,770 --> 00:19:31,740
Why are you suddenly concerned
about Park Min Jun?

318
00:19:32,940 --> 00:19:33,940
Just because.

319
00:19:34,780 --> 00:19:36,210
The chairman election is coming up.

320
00:19:37,180 --> 00:19:38,280
That's why.

321
00:19:43,690 --> 00:19:44,690
Right.

322
00:19:45,060 --> 00:19:47,720
Save the sentimental
and complex thoughts for later,

323
00:19:48,290 --> 00:19:50,460
after Hyun Jun becomes chairman.

324
00:19:51,360 --> 00:19:53,530
Hyun Jun, wait for me.

325
00:19:56,830 --> 00:19:58,570
Keep a close watch...

326
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:00,600
on your designated posts.

327
00:20:00,770 --> 00:20:01,870
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

328
00:20:06,010 --> 00:20:08,450
I told your mother
to wait in the car.

329
00:20:08,880 --> 00:20:10,650
Hyun Jun, you go wait
in the car too.

330
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:12,950
I'll stand guard here.

331
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:15,020
I don't need your help.

332
00:20:16,150 --> 00:20:17,520
When the blackmailer shows up,

333
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:19,590
I'll catch him myself,
grab the phone,

334
00:20:21,560 --> 00:20:23,360
and win my father's approval.

335
00:20:39,140 --> 00:20:42,950
This is the Swiss bank
where Park Tae Ho holds his slush fund.

336
00:20:43,350 --> 00:20:44,720
Identity verification is handled...

337
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:46,880
by a dedicated banker
who visits in person.

338
00:20:48,220 --> 00:20:50,350
Should Manager Kang change his mind,

339
00:20:50,850 --> 00:20:53,490
be prepared to assume control
of the account immediately.

340
00:20:54,860 --> 00:20:57,690
Sure. I'll get that set up.

341
00:20:58,600 --> 00:20:59,800
Ms. Kim,

342
00:21:00,630 --> 00:21:04,530
your task is to get Manager Kang
to betray Park Tae Ho.

343
00:21:05,340 --> 00:21:06,340
Right.

344
00:21:06,870 --> 00:21:08,440
It's probably well underway.

345
00:21:28,660 --> 00:21:30,660
Didn't you hit him too hard?

346
00:21:30,660 --> 00:21:33,700
Don't worry.
I just tapped a pressure point,

347
00:21:33,760 --> 00:21:34,970
so he'll wake up in a bit.

348
00:21:36,670 --> 00:21:38,740
- Out of the way.
- Here.

349
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:42,610
Here. Get him in the car.

350
00:21:43,070 --> 00:21:45,080
- In the back seat.
- Got it.

351
00:21:45,210 --> 00:21:47,340
- Yoon Jung, watch your step.
- Sure.

352
00:21:48,210 --> 00:21:51,010
- James, you be careful too.
- Stop that, will you?

353
00:21:51,010 --> 00:21:54,180
Quit flirting, you two, and focus.
All right?

354
00:21:54,520 --> 00:21:57,220
I'm bitter enough as it is
that I was the last...

355
00:21:57,620 --> 00:21:59,720
to find out about you two.

356
00:22:01,260 --> 00:22:02,260
Who cares?

357
00:22:03,990 --> 00:22:05,030
Who cares?

358
00:22:17,940 --> 00:22:20,110
We secured the bag of money.

359
00:22:20,740 --> 00:22:24,150
Park Tae Ho's probably losing his mind
over losing all that cash.

360
00:22:24,310 --> 00:22:26,080
Plus, we planted the phone
just like we planned.

361
00:22:26,080 --> 00:22:30,120
So, is making Park Tae Ho
suspect Manager Kang the next step?

362
00:22:36,630 --> 00:22:37,660
What?

363
00:22:38,100 --> 00:22:42,900
How the heck do you lose a bag
containing ten million dollars?

364
00:22:44,970 --> 00:22:48,140
I'm sorry, sir! Please forgive me.

365
00:22:48,210 --> 00:22:51,810
Forgive you? You lost money
that's worth more than your life,

366
00:22:52,180 --> 00:22:53,710
and you have the nerve to say that?

367
00:22:53,810 --> 00:22:55,210
What on earth?

368
00:22:55,780 --> 00:22:58,350
What do you mean
the money bag was stolen?

369
00:22:58,420 --> 00:23:00,550
Who on earth snatched it?

370
00:23:00,620 --> 00:23:04,050
- I have no idea.
- You pathetic fool!

371
00:23:04,120 --> 00:23:07,190
See what happens when you try
to do things without me?

372
00:23:09,560 --> 00:23:10,830
Times like these...

373
00:23:10,990 --> 00:23:14,000
call for a much sharper analysis
of the situation.

374
00:23:14,900 --> 00:23:15,900
What?

375
00:23:16,530 --> 00:23:20,140
My cop instincts are telling me
there's definitely more to this.

376
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:22,370
What more could there be?

377
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:24,440
Did the blackmailer show up
at the warehouse or not?

378
00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:29,310
- He didn't.
- Did the blackmailer call?

379
00:23:30,010 --> 00:23:32,020
Didn't he call asking
where the money is...

380
00:23:32,150 --> 00:23:36,220
and why you had people waiting
to trap him?

381
00:23:41,190 --> 00:23:44,090
Now that you mention it,
there's been no contact.

382
00:23:45,460 --> 00:23:46,800
Then that means...

383
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:49,700
I think he's the one
who took the bag of money.

384
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:52,100
He must've known people were hiding
in the warehouse...

385
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:54,300
and taken it in advance!

386
00:23:58,980 --> 00:24:00,310
Did you say it happened
in the parking lot?

387
00:24:01,180 --> 00:24:02,210
Let's see your car.

388
00:24:02,580 --> 00:24:04,750
The dashcam might've
recorded something.

389
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:22,000
Well, it's been completely erased.

390
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:27,640
That just makes this
even more suspicious.

391
00:24:27,770 --> 00:24:30,110
I never even laid a finger on it.

392
00:24:44,820 --> 00:24:47,660
Hello, Mr. Choi Sam Sik.
This is Daebong Capital.

393
00:24:48,360 --> 00:24:50,630
I'm calling about
the eligibility requirements...

394
00:24:50,630 --> 00:24:52,960
for an additional loan
that you asked about.

395
00:24:55,070 --> 00:24:59,170
So, this is Choi Sam Sik's phone?

396
00:25:00,940 --> 00:25:02,510
What did you just say?

397
00:25:08,850 --> 00:25:10,450
You're busted.

398
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:14,420
- But...
- Sir!

399
00:25:14,420 --> 00:25:16,520
Detective Yun!

400
00:25:21,790 --> 00:25:24,230
That detective on the other end
answered the phone.

401
00:25:24,390 --> 00:25:25,600
That corrupt detective?

402
00:25:25,660 --> 00:25:28,200
This might actually work
in our favor.

403
00:25:28,670 --> 00:25:30,070
If the detective gets involved,

404
00:25:30,070 --> 00:25:32,640
he'll frame Manager Kang
as the culprit.

405
00:25:35,010 --> 00:25:37,310
Then it's my turn to make a move.

406
00:25:51,390 --> 00:25:54,660
Manager Kang was in possession
of Choi Sam Sik's cell phone.

407
00:25:56,090 --> 00:25:58,800
There's no recording of the call,

408
00:25:59,200 --> 00:26:01,600
so he must've used a fake voice
to threaten you.

409
00:26:04,630 --> 00:26:07,440
What are you talking about?

410
00:26:07,600 --> 00:26:11,070
You orchestrated this whole thing!

411
00:26:15,010 --> 00:26:18,580
Manager Kang, you... You!

412
00:26:19,080 --> 00:26:22,250
That isn't true.
I had nothing to do with this.

413
00:26:23,390 --> 00:26:26,220
Father, let me figure out
what actually happened first.

414
00:26:26,220 --> 00:26:27,960
You lying backstabber!

415
00:26:32,800 --> 00:26:33,930
Father!

416
00:26:35,100 --> 00:26:39,070
You stole Choi Sam Sik's phone,
blackmailed me,

417
00:26:39,440 --> 00:26:40,840
and took my money!

418
00:26:42,340 --> 00:26:45,410
That isn't true.
Please believe me, sir.

419
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:48,210
How could I orchestrate
something like this?

420
00:26:49,310 --> 00:26:51,610
You would
because that's just who you are.

421
00:26:53,020 --> 00:26:55,890
I knew from the beginning
that you were a two-faced snake.

422
00:26:56,690 --> 00:26:57,850
Just look at
what happened last time.

423
00:26:58,290 --> 00:27:00,620
After drawing up
a power of attorney for me,

424
00:27:00,660 --> 00:27:03,330
you stabbed me in the back
the moment he woke up.

425
00:27:04,690 --> 00:27:07,500
That was because
you were hurting the chairman...

426
00:27:07,500 --> 00:27:08,530
Shut it!

427
00:27:12,270 --> 00:27:15,910
I don't need excuses,
so bring it back right now!

428
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:19,210
- What?
- The ten million dollars.

429
00:27:19,780 --> 00:27:22,710
Get my ten million back here
right now.

430
00:27:23,250 --> 00:27:26,650
Just bring the money back,
and I'll forgive you this one time.

431
00:27:27,020 --> 00:27:28,550
Get it here right now.

432
00:27:28,690 --> 00:27:30,720
My men will be on you,

433
00:27:31,350 --> 00:27:33,090
so don't get any funny ideas.

434
00:27:34,160 --> 00:27:35,990
Just bring back my money!

435
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:39,400
Sir...

436
00:27:41,770 --> 00:27:42,770
Darn it!

437
00:27:47,800 --> 00:27:51,710
(Park Tae Ho)

438
00:28:07,660 --> 00:28:08,660
Yes?

439
00:28:08,960 --> 00:28:11,800
It's Kim Dan Hui.
Can we meet for a moment?

440
00:28:20,270 --> 00:28:21,440
Mom, do you really think...

441
00:28:21,970 --> 00:28:23,910
Manager Kang betrayed Father?

442
00:28:25,140 --> 00:28:26,540
Whether it's true or not,

443
00:28:27,810 --> 00:28:30,680
we have to make it true.
This is our chance.

444
00:28:31,980 --> 00:28:32,980
Our chance?

445
00:28:33,980 --> 00:28:35,050
If Manager Kang gets booted,

446
00:28:35,120 --> 00:28:36,950
who do you think
will manage the slush fund?

447
00:28:37,890 --> 00:28:39,390
That was originally my job anyway.

448
00:28:40,490 --> 00:28:43,630
I'm going to take this chance
to get the slush fund ledger back.

449
00:28:44,360 --> 00:28:47,200
Then I can have both the slush fund
and the ledger in my hands.

450
00:28:48,670 --> 00:28:50,470
I'll be sure to get them back,

451
00:28:50,970 --> 00:28:51,970
so you just wait.

452
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:01,240
Something seems...

453
00:29:03,010 --> 00:29:04,180
a little off.

454
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:17,830
That Manager Kang...

455
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:21,660
How dare he betray me?

456
00:29:23,230 --> 00:29:27,370
He's the same guy who betrayed you
when I took you down.

457
00:29:28,570 --> 00:29:31,940
Betrayal always comes
from those closest to you.

458
00:29:33,340 --> 00:29:35,950
He was the first to suggest
paying off the blackmailer.

459
00:29:36,780 --> 00:29:40,120
On top of that, we haven't heard
from the blackmailer since.

460
00:29:43,090 --> 00:29:44,350
That being said,

461
00:29:45,050 --> 00:29:49,030
can't you put me back in charge
of the slush fund?

462
00:29:49,530 --> 00:29:50,530
What?

463
00:29:51,090 --> 00:29:53,800
Put the woman who tried to kill me
back in charge?

464
00:29:54,360 --> 00:29:56,430
That's all water under the bridge.

465
00:29:56,970 --> 00:29:59,540
Our Hyun Jun is going to be
the chairman of Adele Group.

466
00:29:59,600 --> 00:30:01,500
How could I stab you in the back?

467
00:30:01,640 --> 00:30:04,110
Even so, Oh Jung Ran,
it can't be you.

468
00:30:05,310 --> 00:30:06,310
Then what?

469
00:30:06,780 --> 00:30:08,440
Will you keep letting
Manager Kang handle it?

470
00:30:09,750 --> 00:30:12,080
Are you really going to forgive him
if he brings back...

471
00:30:12,580 --> 00:30:13,650
the ten million dollars?

472
00:30:14,620 --> 00:30:17,020
If he shows up with the cash,
he's a traitor.

473
00:30:17,190 --> 00:30:20,660
If he doesn't, he's just pathetic.

474
00:30:22,030 --> 00:30:24,860
Either way, he's useless to me now,
so I need to get rid of him.

475
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:28,000
How are you going to do that?

476
00:30:28,730 --> 00:30:30,030
The same way as always.

477
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:35,000
He knows too much to be left alive.

478
00:30:36,410 --> 00:30:39,310
I'll immediately change the name
on the dummy account,

479
00:30:40,740 --> 00:30:41,780
and then deal with him.

480
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:09,070
You have a visitor.

481
00:31:20,050 --> 00:31:21,080
You're here.

482
00:31:21,520 --> 00:31:22,650
Have you made a decision?

483
00:31:23,190 --> 00:31:24,190
Yes.

484
00:31:24,690 --> 00:31:26,590
If you can guarantee
my safety and my family's,

485
00:31:28,090 --> 00:31:29,090
I'll do it.

486
00:31:30,890 --> 00:31:32,200
The chairman's slush fund...

487
00:31:34,260 --> 00:31:35,270
I'll drain it for you.

488
00:32:08,770 --> 00:32:11,670
(Pearl in Red)

489
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:14,600
What? Kim Dan Hui cleaned out
the slush fund?

490
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:19,680
You actually went so far
as to betray your own father?

491
00:32:19,840 --> 00:32:21,480
- Father!
- Honey!

492
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:24,650
Mr. Kim, it won't be
that much longer now.

493
00:32:25,180 --> 00:32:28,320
The day I clear your name...

494
00:32:28,890 --> 00:32:30,390
isn't far off.

495
00:32:31,050 --> 00:32:33,020
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
